Text: Chairmans AwardMrs Lay and Skilling Thank you I just received my tshirt and letter regarding the Chairmans award nomination I was really flattered to have received that mention The traits sought by the Chairmans award are those I would really like to exemplify respect communication integrity and excellence To even have been considered worthy is exciting and humbling I know that truly most people at Enron hope to display these values and for you to have designed an award to recognize them is really inspiring In short it meant a lot to me to have been mentioned for the Chairmans award within a company of which I am so proud I know it will mean a great deal to the person I will seek to nominate when I next have the opportunity Thank you Sincerely Julia Cobb
